Package: aLBI
Type: Package
Title: aLBI - a simple r package for estimating Length-Based Indicators and Fish Stock Assessment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ataher", "Ali", email = "ataher.cu.ms@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Alam", "Mohammed Shahidul", email = "alamms@cu.ac.bd", role = "aut")
)

Maintainer: Ataher Ali <ataher.cu.ms@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides tools for calculating length-based indicators for fish stock assessment using length frequency data and bootstrap resampling. It includes functions for data validation, parameter estimation, and stock status assessment.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    dplyr, 
    ggplot2, 
    readxl, 
    stats
